description: Dannii Minogue - Love And Kisses (1991) FLAC Love and Kisses is the international debut studio album by Australian singer Dannii Minogue. It was released by MCA Records on 3 June 1991, in the United Kingdom. It contains a very similar track listing to the Australian debut album, Dannii, and was issued with different artwork and additional tracks. In August 1991, the album was certified Gold in the UK.
